            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay"><div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/07/06/2023-07-06T095711Z146467102RC2LX1AAYPD6RTRMADP3CHINA-USA-YELLEN.JPG?VersionId=7WpDWyeThC0LVwdHvbhjTyX4gLaIL.Lq&amp;itok=AX9l1Pfs" alt="" data-caption="耶伦抵达北京后，在接机人员陪同下步行离开。（路透社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/07/06/2023-07-06T095711Z146467102RC2LX1AAYPD6RTRMADP3CHINA-USA-YELLEN.JPG?VersionId=7WpDWyeThC0LVwdHvbhjTyX4gLaIL.Lq&amp;itok=AX9l1Pfs" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div> <figcaption><p>耶伦抵达北京后，在接机人员陪同下步行离开。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div><div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div></div>     <p>美国财政部长耶伦星期四（7月6日）下午抵达北京，开启访华之旅。</p><p>中国央视新闻星期四下午5时15分左右发布耶伦乘机抵达北京的消息。</p><p>中央广播电视总台旗下微博账号“玉渊谭天”消息称，中国财政部国际经济关系司司长杨英明到场接机。&nbsp;</p><section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1"></div></section><p>彭博社此前引述耶伦的办公室报道，耶伦预计在新加坡时间星期四下午4时半抵达北京，之后会与中国高级官员会面。</p> <figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/articles/2023/07/06/2023-07-05T121943Z1426659240RC20X1AX5OITRTRMADP3CHINA-USA-YELLEN_3.JPG?VersionId=QH5lUTPbE3YC395k_ipPRlLv5uZuobXS" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"> <figcaption>耶伦当地时间星期三（7月5日）从马里兰州安德鲁斯联合基地启程，前往北京访问。（路透社）</figcaption></figure><div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sph-brightcove-video paragraph--view-mode--default"><div class="field field--name-field-media-sph-brightcove field--type-string field--label-visually_hidden"><div class="field__item"><div class="sph-media-brightcove-outer-wrapper" id="media-brightcove-725519"><div class="sph-media-brightcove-preview-wrapper" id="sph_media_brightcove_6330665514112_725519"><div style="display: 